title.en: Ane no Migawari de Konyaku shitara Naze ka Henkyou no Seijo to Yobareru you ni narimashita
Himegimi wa Wakaki Shougun ni Oboreru
Sono Akuyaku Reijou wa Kouryakuhon wo Tazusaete iru
Rekishi ni Nokoru Akujo ni naru zo
Futsutsukana Akujo de wa Gozaimasu ga
Konyaku Haki no Juubun Mae ni, Zense wo Omoidashimashita
Akuyaku Reijou (Yotei) Rashii kedo, Watashi wa Okashi ga Tabetai
Cheat Shoujo ga Boukun Seiou ni Dekiai saresou desu ga, Ima wa Mahou ni Muchuu nan desu!!!
Akuyaku Reijou ni Erabareta nara, Yuuga ni Enjite Misemashou!
Hametsu End Kara Gyakkou Shitara, Nishuume wa Nazeka Aisare Route deshita - Yami Ochi Reijou wa Ouji e no Fukushuu wo Akiramenai (no ni Dekiaisareru)
Akuyaku Reijou ni Naritakunai node Ouji-sama to Issho ni Kanpeki Reijou wo Mezashimasu!
Ouhi ni Naru Yotei Deshita ga, Nise Seijo no Omei wo Kiserareta no de Toubou Shitara, Koutaishi ni Dekiai Saremashita. Sochira mo Douzo Oshiawase ni
Kyuukoku no Seijo Desuga, Kokugai Tsuihou Sarechaimashita?!
Shukujo no Kagami Yamemashita. Toki wo Gyakkou shita Koushaku Reijou wa, Wagamama na Imouto ni Furimawasarenai you Seikaku Waruku Ikinobimasu!
Migawari no Hanayome wa, Bukiyou na Henkyou Haku ni Dekiaisareru
